/ ============================================================
/ LÓGICA DE GEOMETRÍA (Modificable en la presentación)
/ ============================================================
CHECK_SHAPE, HEX 000
/ --- FIGURA: TRIÁNGULO PIRÁMIDE ---
LOAD COL
SUBT MITAD
JNS ABS_VAL
STORE TMP
LOAD FILA
SUBT TMP
SKIPCOND 000       / Si AC >= 0, está dentro
JUMP IS_INSIDE
LOAD ZERO
JUMPI CHECK_SHAPE
IS_INSIDE,   LOAD ONE
JUMPI CHECK_SHAPE

ABS_VAL,     HEX 000            / Subrutina Valor Absoluto
SKIPCOND 000
JUMPI ABS_VAL
STORE TMP
LOAD ZERO
SUBT TMP
JUMPI ABS_VAL

/ ============================================================
/ INICIO DEL PROGRAMA (Sintaxis Corregida línea por línea)
/ ============================================================
START,       JNS MSG_START
LOAD ZERO
STORE SCORE
JNS INIT_BOARD     /
JNS CALC_SAFE      /
JUMP RENDER        /

MSG_START,   HEX 000
LOAD ASC_S
OUTPUT
LOAD ASC_T
OUTPUT
LOAD ASC_A
OUTPUT
LOAD ASC_R
OUTPUT
LOAD ASC_T
OUTPUT
JUMPI MSG_START

/ ============================================================
/ BUCLE PRINCIPAL
/ ============================================================
MAIN_LOOP,   INPUT
STORE FILA
INPUT
STORE COL
INPUT
STORE ACCION
JNS CALC_IDX

JNS CHECK_SHAPE    / Filtro de geometría
SKIPCOND 800
JUMP MAIN_LOOP

LOAD ACCION
SUBT ONE
SKIPCOND 400
JUMP DO_FLAG
JUMP DO_REVEAL

/ --- Lógica de Banderas y Puntaje ---
DO_FLAG,     JNS FLG_LOGIC
JUMP RENDER

FLG_LOGIC,   HEX 000
LOAD INDEX
ADD B_VIS
STORE DIR
LOADI DIR
STORE TMP
SUBT ST_REVEAL
SKIPCOND 400
JUMP FLG_TOGGLE
JUMPI FLG_LOGIC

FLG_TOGGLE,  LOAD TMP
SUBT ST_FLAG
SKIPCOND 400
JUMP ADD_FLG
/ Quitar Bandera
LOAD ST_HIDDEN
STOREI DIR
JNS UPD_SCORE_NEG
JUMP FLG_OUT
/ Poner Bandera
ADD_FLG,     LOAD ST_FLAG
STOREI DIR
JNS UPD_SCORE_POS
FLG_OUT,     LOAD SCORE
OUTPUT             / Puntaje actual en consola
JUMPI FLG_LOGIC

UPD_SCORE_POS, HEX 000
LOAD INDEX
ADD B_REAL
STORE TMP
LOADI TMP
SKIPCOND 000     / ¿Es mina (-1)?
JUMP INC_S
JUMPI UPD_SCORE_POS
INC_S,         LOAD SCORE
ADD ONE
STORE SCORE
JUMPI UPD_SCORE_POS

UPD_SCORE_NEG, HEX 000
LOAD INDEX
ADD B_REAL
STORE TMP
LOADI TMP
SKIPCOND 000
JUMP DEC_S
JUMPI UPD_SCORE_NEG
DEC_S,         LOAD SCORE
SUBT ONE
STORE SCORE
JUMPI UPD_SCORE_NEG

/ --- Otras subrutinas (Mantenidas para funcionalidad completa) ---
/ (Incluye aquí CALC_IDX, INIT_BOARD, GET_COORDS, RENDER del histórico)